PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1996-2011 of December 19, 1996 respecting the reappointment of J. CLIFFORD McISAAC as a member and chairman of the National Farm Products Council by revoking the words "for a term ending March 31, 1997" and substituting the words "to hold office during pleasure, until the appointment of a successor".
